"title": "4287: universe",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "4287",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>All existing things, including the earth and its creatures and all the heavenly bodies. The universe was made by God and is sustained by Jesus Christ.</p>\n<h2>God as the Maker of all things</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:15\">PSA 115:15</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:16\">JER 10:16</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:11\">REV 4:11</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen14:19\">GEN 14:19</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:15\">2KI 19:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eccl11:5\">ECC 11:5</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:16\">ISA 37:16</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa44:24\">ISA 44:24</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom11:33-Rom11:36\">ROM 11:33–11:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph3:9\">EPH 3:9</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb11:3\">HEB 11:3</a></p>\n<h2>God as the ruler of the universe</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:12\">1CH 29:12</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:24\">ACT 17:24</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps119:91\">PSA 119:91</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer33:25\">JER 33:25</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt11:25\">MAT 11:25</a></p>\n<h2>Jesus Christ, the one through whom the universe was made, now sustains all things</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:3\">JHN 1:3</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Col1:15-Col1:17\">COL 1:15–1:17</a></strong> <em>The title “firstborn” implies that Jesus Christ is the heir, that everything belongs to him</em>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:2-Heb1:3\">HEB 1:2–1:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John13:3\">JHN 13:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:22\">EPH 1:22</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph4:10\">EPH 4:10</a></p>\n<h2>The universe is temporary</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:35\">MAT 24:35</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:10-2Pet3:12\">2PE 3:10–3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt5:18\">MAT 5:18</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt24:29\">MAT 24:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Luke21:26\">LUK 21:26</a></p>\n<h2>Future renewal of the universe</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Pet3:13\">2PE 3:13</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa65:17\">ISA 65:17</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa66:22\">ISA 66:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt19:28\">MAT 19:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom8:19-Rom8:22\">ROM 8:19–8:22</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Eph1:10\">EPH 1:10</a></p>\n<h2>Other references to the universe</h2>\n<p><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut4:25-Deut4:26\">DEU 4:25–4:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:19\">DEU 30:19</a>; ; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Phil2:15\">PHP 2:15</a></p>",
